    "body": "fixes https://github.com/LLNL/spack/issues/4529\r\n\r\nSince sorting one way or the other didn't seem to be a big deal, I adjusted logic so that variants are displayed during `spack info` in the order a package declares them.\r\n\r\nThis required me to add a member to a variant indicating its declaration order. Didn't see a cleaner way to handle it.",
